text: The Fermon ( ATCC , VR - 1826 ) , US / KY / 14 - 18953 ( ATCC , VR - 1825D ) , and US / MO / 14 - 18947 ( ATCC , VR - 1823D ) strains of EV - D68 ; and the Changchun077 strain of EV - A71 have been reported previously ( Wang et al . , 2012 ) . Viruses were propagated in human rhabdomyosarcoma , and the supernatants were harvested and stored at − 80 • C . Human embryonic kidney cells ( HEK 293T cells ) ( No CRL - 11268 ) and RD cells were purchased from the ATCC ( Manassas , VA , USA ) and used according to a previous study . Cells were maintained in Dulbecco ' s modified Eagle ' s medium ( DMEM ) ( Hyclone , Logan , UT , USA ) supplemented with 10 % fetal bovine serum ( FBS ) ( GIBCO BRL , Grand Island , NY , USA ) .
